The Java solution for the problem to determine whether an integer n is a power of three can be implemented as follows:

```java
public static boolean isPowerOfThree(int n) {
    if (n < 0 || n > 0x7FFFFFFF) {
        return false;
    }
    if (n == 1 || n == 3) {
        return true;
    }
    int x = 3;
    while (n != 0 && x != 0) {
        if (n % x == 0) {
            n /= x;
        } else {
            x *= x;
        }
    }
    return n == 0 && x != 0;
}
```

